<subSubSection id="5DCA0485FFD5FFABB1AD56BCFD29FE1E" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="156F570EFFD5FFABB1AD56BCFB88FED2" blockId="90.[151,1437,151,537]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFD5FFABB1AD56BCFEF5FF37" bold="true" box="[199,345,222,248]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Distribution</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFD5FFABB00D56BDFD2CFF36" box="[359,640,223,249]" class="Insecta" family="Pseudococcidae" genus="Phenacoccus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arthrophyti">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFD5FFABB00D56BDFD2CFF36" box="[359,640,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Phenacoccus arthrophyti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from six Palaearctic countries including 
<collectingCountry id="6DC7179EFFD5FFABB5D956BDFB4CFF36" box="[1203,1248,223,249]" name="Iran" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFD5FFABB58456BDFEBEFED1" author="Garcia Morales M. &amp; Denno, B. D. &amp; Miller, D. R. &amp; Miller, G. L. &amp; Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B." pageId="90" pageNumber="91" refId="ref89637" refString="Garcia Morales M., Denno, B. D., Miller, D. R., Miller, G. L., Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B. (2016) ScaleNet: a literature-based model of scale insect biology and systematics. Database. Available from: http: // scalenet. info (accessed 30 January 2021) https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / database / bav 118" type="url" year="2016">
García Morales 
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFD5FFABB1FD5761FF64FED2" box="[151,200,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
), where it has been recorded from 
<collectingRegion id="D71499ECFFD5FFABB3FF5761FC9AFED2" box="[661,822,259,285]" country="Iran" name="Yazd" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Yazd province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFD5FFABB22F5761FBB4FED2" author="Moghaddam, M." box="[837,1048,259,285]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" pagination="37 - 38" refId="ref94511" refString="Moghaddam, M. (2003) New record of three scale insects (Hem.: Coccoidea) from Iran. Applied Entomology and Phytopathology, 71 (1), 37 - 38." type="journal article" year="2003">Moghaddam 2003</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="156F570EFFD5FFABB1AD5745FE6CFE46" blockId="90.[151,1437,151,537]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFD5FFABB1AD5745FEFDFE8E" bold="true" box="[199,337,295,321]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Host-plants</emphasis>
: This species has been recorded on host-plants in seven genera belonging to the families 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFD5FFABB4535745FF47FEAA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Amaranthaceae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFD5FFABB0495729FD41FEA9" authority="(Garcia Morales et al. 2016)" baseAuthorityName="Garcia Morales" baseAuthorityYear="2016" box="[291,749,331,358]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">
Asteraceae (
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFD5FFABB0C45729FD4AFEA9" author="Garcia Morales M. &amp; Denno, B. D. &amp; Miller, D. R. &amp; Miller, G. L. &amp; Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B." box="[430,742,331,358]" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" refId="ref89637" refString="Garcia Morales M., Denno, B. D., Miller, D. R., Miller, G. L., Ben-Dov, Y. &amp; Hardy, N. B. (2016) ScaleNet: a literature-based model of scale insect biology and systematics. Database. Available from: http: // scalenet. info (accessed 30 January 2021) https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / database / bav 118" type="url" year="2016">
García Morales 
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFD5FFABB30D5729FD35FEAA" box="[615,665,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. In 
<collectingCountry id="6DC7179EFFD5FFABB2735729FCE5FEAA" box="[793,841,331,357]" name="Iran" pageId="90" pageNumber="91">Iran</collectingCountry>
, it has been recorded on 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFD5FFABB5025729FAA9FEAA" box="[1128,1285,331,357]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Haloxylon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="90" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
